The use of randomized algorithms and high-performance computing platforms also suggests a potential fit for cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) sub-categories. However, based on the content of the paper, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.LG, and cs.CV seem to be the most relevant sub-categories.
